Monitor-off.content: Under most circumstances your monitor has to be on for Natro to work. The macro not working with your monitor off is not a bug or a glitch. It is your system not providing a signal for Natro to work properly. If you want to run Natro with your screen off, consider using a RDP, though keep in mind this is an advanced feature, meaning it's not meant for everyone: some computer knowledge is required. <#1069024541935927316>

RDP-TCPV6.content: Roblox uses a 32-bit internet protocol (TCPv4), which means having a 128-bit internet protocol (TCPv6) can cause compatibility issues, such as input lag. Turning it off won't help, you must disable it entirely. Otherwise, buying a new router that deals with this issue or updating the firmware for your current router may fix it. To fix the input lag, run ``cmd prompt`` as administrator, type in this message: ```reg add "HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SYSTEM\CurrentControlSet\Services\Tcpip6\Parameters" /v DisabledComponents /t REG_DWORD /d 255 /f``` and send enter, and then restart your computer afterwards.

Remote-control-(RC).content: The macro can be partially controled with commands sent through Discord. This feature allow you to control a variety of things\, such as changing variables or even remote reconnection. You can find a guide and troubleshooting steps [here](https://discord.com/channels/1012610056921038868/1191570640596111461)

Videos.content:
Providing a video can help out discover the problem a LOT quicker. Here are some ways you can record videos in a format that is viewable on discord with decent quality:

[OBS](https://cdn-fastly.obsproject.com/downloads/OBS-Studio-29.1.3-Full-Installer-x64.exe/), all around most flexible option
[NVIDIA screen capture](https://www.nvidia.com/en-us/geforce/geforce-experience/shadowplay/#download), built into nvidia drivers by default
[Xbox gamebar](https://apps.microsoft.com/store/detail/xbox-game-bar/9NZKPSTSNW4P?hl=en-us&gl=us), easily most accessible, winkey+g
[Gyazo](https://gyazo.com/signup), short gifs can be useful
[Medal](https://medal.tv/download?start), can cause false postives in antiviruses and has a lot of bloat
[Outplayed](https://download.overwolf.com/install/Download?Name=Outplayed&ExtensionId=cghphpbjeabdkomiphingnegihoigeggcfphdofo&Channel=web_dl_btn&utm_content=newoneapp), requires overwolf & has ads

Note: videos in .wmv (format of roblox's built in recorder) and .mkv (default OBS video format) cannot be embedded into discord. If you do have a file with this format though, you can always convert it to .mp4 using [CloudConvert](https://cloudconvert.com;CloudConvert)
